# PLAYER::GET_NUMBER_OF_PLAYERS

## Summary
Gets the number of players

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the number of players in the current session.
If not multiplayer, always returns 1.
